item.title: By: Raptor
item.dc:creator: Raptor
item.description:
True that on the marriage - we had a guy in Lineage II - lost his bgrade because gf put in a call to CS that she played his char (didn't ever touch, but he logged from her house while we all sat around) & gave her ip & his ip - bam all three of his legit accounts banned.
No he's just got 2 accounts with his farmer & his pker. He's been hunting the bitch for a month now. Delevelled her 5 times, she sits & tries to go toe to toe, then sits in town & screams at him after he kills her instead of log.
